erformance-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/TiestoteasesGlastonbury-performance-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/TiestoteasesGlastonbury-performance-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/TiestoteasesGlastonbury-performance-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/tisto">蒂斯托（Tiësto）</a>在<a href="https://www.nme.com/glastonbury-2025">2025年格拉斯顿伯里（Glastonbury）节</a>上取笑了可能的演出。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/glastonbury-2025-headliners-rumours-3773153"><b>谁能成为格拉斯顿伯里（Glastonbury）2025：到目前为止的顶级跑步者和车手</b></a></strong></li></ul><p>在 <a href="https://www.globalplayer.com/catchup/capital/uk/b8G4xFf/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">首都英国</a><em>与吉米·希尔（Jimmy Hill）的晚间演出</em>的新采访中，荷兰DJ和制片人被问到他是否有计划返回英国的节日季节。</p><p>他回答说：“我现在正在研究它，所以我还没有真正制定计划。” “但是也许奶油菲尔德也许是格拉斯顿伯里（Glastonbury），我正在与所有这些家伙聊天，所以我们会看到。试图找到生活中的平衡！”</p><p>持有<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/grammys">格莱美奖</a>的Trance艺术家此前曾在传奇的值得农场活动中演出。他曾多次出现在Creamfields的法案上， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/calvin-harris-swedish-house-mafia-and-tiesto-to-headline-creamfields-south-2023-3355094">最后一条在2023年成为EDM音乐节</a>。</p><p> Tiësto于同年发行了他的第七张和最新录音室专辑“ Drive”。该唱片与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/charli-xcx">Charli XCX</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/black-eyed-peas">Black Eyed Peas</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/tate-mcrae">Tate McRae</a>之类的合作进行了合作。</p><p>去年， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/tiesto-will-be-super-bowls-first-ever-in-game-dj-3577779">蒂斯托（Tiësto）计划在拉斯维加斯（Las Vegas）担任超级碗的首个游戏中DJ</a> ，但<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kaskade-to-replace-tiesto-as-first-super-bowl-dj-after-personal-family-emergency-3585048">由于“个人家庭紧急情况”，这位明星被迫退出</a>。他被Kaskade取代。</p><p> Glastonbury 2025将于6月25日至6月29日之间举行。上个月，组织者<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/neil-young-confirmed-to-headline-glastonbury-2025-after-pulling-out-3825853">确认尼尔·杨（Neil Young）是今年夏天的第一个金字塔舞台头条新闻</a>，此前<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/neil-young-pulls-out-of-glastonbury-2025-it-is-a-corporate-turn-off-3825496">音乐家最初退出了车位</a>。</p><p>由于与<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/bbc">英国广播公司</a>的合作伙伴关系，他称格拉斯托为“公司关闭”。但是，年轻的后来回溯，并以“收到的信息错误”为主题。歌手兼作曲家于2009年首次成为格拉斯顿伯里（Glastonbury）的头条新闻。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DEXQKOLIC4v/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.34