eadliners-rumours-3773153">在此处阅读<em>NME</em>的潜在头条新闻的完整列表</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-festival-2025-tickets-buy-how-to-price-line-up-faq-3809687">预计将在春季开始销售售票</a>。<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-tickets-sell-out-in-35-minutes-3813419">去年11月，最初的门票很快就卖光了</a>，音乐节<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-festival-2025-tickets-buy-how-to-price-line-up-faq-3809687">利用新的排队系统进行预订</a>。</p><p>在其他新闻中， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/want-to-play-glastonbury-2025-this-years-emerging-talent-competition-has-launched-3830682">格拉斯顿伯里（Glastonbury）最近启动了今年的新兴人才竞赛</a>，这使新艺术家有机会在今年6月在Worthy Farm演出。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/tiesto-teases-glastonbury-2025-appearance-3835579">Tiësto后戏弄Glastonbury 2025出现</a>在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上首次出现。</p> ;
